# Compiled artifacts — regenerated by `sui move build` / `deploy.sh`
build/

# Written by `sui client publish` after a successful deploy.
# Checked in would cause "Modules must all have 0x0 as their addresses" on redeploy.
Published.toml

# Package metadata, generated by `sui move build` and `sui client publish`.
package_summaries/

docs-site/.cmdocs/